{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 123991,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「千姫さんは戦場をお捨てになったかと思ったから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I thought Lady Senhime had abandoned the battlefield,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123992,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　わたくしのライバルから外していたのに……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so I had removed her from my list of rivals...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123993,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それをまた、こんなあっさりと",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"And yet, to come back so easily like this,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123994,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　戻ってきてらっしゃるなんて……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "returning once again...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123995,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そうか……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I see...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123996,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「私が戻ってきたことを",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You’re happy that I’ve come back,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123997,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　喜んでくれるのか、少し照れるな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I’m a bit embarrassed by that.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123998,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いやいやいや、言ってないですわ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, no, no, I didn’t say that.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123999,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「私も一度は戦を捨て、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I too once abandoned war,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124000,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　母として生きることを決めた身。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "deciding to live as a mother."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124001,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　戻って来る気はなかったんだがな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I had no intention of returning, though.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124002,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ま、こうなった以上は、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, now that things are like this,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124003,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　共に戦場を駆ける仲間として宜しく頼む」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "let’s work together as comrades on the battlefield.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124004,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「えーえー、しっかり働いて頂きますわ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, yes, you’ll be working hard, for sure.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124005,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……ところでそれは何を？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...By the way, what is that?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124006,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「んー？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124007,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "千姫の膝の上にはピグが座っていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A pig was sitting on Senhime’s lap."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124008,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いや、最近は小さくてふにふにしたものを",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, recently I’ve found comfort in holding"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124009,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　抱えている方が落ち着くようになってしまってな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "something small and soft like this.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124010,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そう言いながら千姫が",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saying that, Senhime"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124011,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ピグの小さな頭を優しく撫でる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "gently stroked the pig’s small head."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124012,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「んひひひ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Nnhihihi...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124013,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さ、たまごポーロを食べなさい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Here, eat some egg polo.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124014,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はむはむ、はむはむ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Nom nom, nom nom...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124015,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふむ……こうして見ると、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm... looking at it this way,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124016,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　チルディも小さくてふにふにしてるな……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Tildi is also small and soft...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124017,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "千姫が自分の膝をぽんぽん叩く。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Senhime patted her own lap."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124018,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「座るか？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Want to sit?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124019,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「結構です！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, thank you!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124020,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はあ、本当に母親になってしまったんですのね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, you really have become a mother, haven't you?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124021,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「まあ、そういうことだな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, that’s how it is.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124022,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「敵襲だーーーッ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Enemy attack---!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124023,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おっと、戦闘か……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh, combat, huh...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124024,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「一人の母として過ごす落ち着いた日々にも",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I had just gotten used to the calm days spent as a mother,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124025,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　慣れてきたところだというのにな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but now this.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124026,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「まったく……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Really...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124027,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124028,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……困ったものだ、フフ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...What a troublesome thing, hehe.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124029,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「顔に嬉しくて仕方ないって書いてありますわよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It’s written all over your face that you’re happy.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124030,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「千姫、たのしそうね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Senhime, you look happy.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124031,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おっと……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oops...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124032,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "千姫が出産の準備を進めていた頃――",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "When Senhime was preparing for childbirth――"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124033,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「千姫様……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Lady Senhime..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124034,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　すっかりお腹が大きくなりましたね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Your belly has grown quite large.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124035,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええ、予定ではそろそろ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, it's about time for the birth according to schedule."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124036,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　産まれるだろうとのことです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124037,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "千姫は己の膨らんだ腹を、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Senhime gently and lovingly stroked her swollen belly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124038,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "優しく、愛おしげに撫でた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124039,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「山本殿に続いて千姫殿も……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Following Lord Yamamoto, Lady Senhime as well..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124040,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いや、なにはともあれ、出産はめでたい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Well, in any case, childbirth is a joyous occasion.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124041,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「改めて……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Once again...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124042,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「行くあてのない私を迎えてくれたこと、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Thank you for welcoming me when I had nowhere to go,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124043,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　此度の援助、心より感謝を申し上げます」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and for the support this time, I sincerely appreciate it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124044,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いいえ、とんでもありません」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, not at all.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124045,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「千姫様は先の戦にて",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Lady Senhime has performed heroic deeds many times in the recent war."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124046,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　何度も武功を立てて下さいました。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124047,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　この程度では報いるには足りないくらいです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"This level of assistance is barely enough to repay you.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124048,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「左様。本来なら褒賞として",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Indeed. Originally, you should be rewarded"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124049,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　もっと厚遇をしなければならぬのに……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "with even greater generosity...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124050,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「既に身に余る心遣いをして頂いてます。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You have already shown me more kindness than I deserve."
    }
  ]
}

